<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Blocked - Source Build</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #ea580c 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #f97316;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fef3e2;
            border-left: 4px solid #f97316;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .warning-box h3 {
            color: #ea580c;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .warning-box p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #666;
        }
        .info-list {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-list ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .info-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .info-list li strong {
            color: #333;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #f97316;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #ea580c;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #f97316;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Status Update</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
            
            <p>
                We're writing to inform you that your Source Build account has been <strong>temporarily blocked</strong>.
            </p>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3>Account Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
                <p><strong>Account Type:</strong> <%= accountType %></p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
                <% if (reason) { %>
                <p><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reason %></p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                This action was taken after careful review of your account activity. While your account is blocked, you will not be able to:
            </p>
            
            <div class="info-list">
                <ul>
                    <li>• Access your Source Build dashboard</li>
                    <li>• Place new orders or list products</li>
                    <li>• Send or receive messages</li>
                    <li>• Update your profile information</li>
                    <li>• Process any pending transactions</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <h3>What happens next?</h3>
            
            <p>
                If you believe this action was taken in error or would like to appeal this decision, please contact our support team immediately. We're here to help resolve any issues.
            </p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" class="cta-button">Contact Support</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                When contacting support, please include your account email address and any relevant information that might help us review your case.
            </p>
            
            <p>
                We take account security seriously and work hard to maintain a safe marketplace for all users. We appreciate your understanding and cooperation.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                This email was sent to <%= email %><br>
                You received this email because of a change to your Source Build account status.
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
                © <%= year %> Source Build. All rights reserved.<br>
                <a href="<%= privacyUrl %>">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="<%= termsUrl %>">Terms of Service</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>